Welcome to the repository for BC-Hadoop 2.0
=================================

BC-Hadoop is the release codes of hadoop runs in China Mobile Research Institute(CMRI), which includes Hadoop, HBase and Zookeeper.

This code is based on Cloudera's Hadoop Distribution (CDH4.3).

More information about BigCloud Project in CMRI is available at http://www.big-cloud.cn/

Development Prerequisites
===========================
OS: RedHat or CentOs 64bit
JDK 1.6.0+
Ant
Maven

